    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "with copy to the Oklahoma City Office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "On 12/8/58 [REDACTED] Oklahoma City, Oklahoma, was contacted by SA [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "and advised that the FBI has not discouraged the investiga-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "tion of flying saucers and that the FBI does not conduct",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "investigation concerning unidentified flying objects (UFO).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] who advised he is 13 years of age,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "stated he had read reports in some of the literature concern-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "ing UFO which indicated that the FBI had discouraged some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "of the investigators from carrying out their research. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "exhibited a copy of a publication entitled \"The Saucerian",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Bulletin\" which could not be given to the interviewing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Agent since he had borrowed the publication from an unidenti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "fied friend. An examination of the publication reflected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "it to be Vol. 3, #4, Released October 15, 1958, edited and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "published by [REDACTED] West Virginia.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The publication consisted of approximately 30 pages, contained",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "several book reviews and advertisements for books pertaining",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "to UFO. Page 20 of the publication contained an editorial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "by [REDACTED] consisting in part of a letter which [REDACTED] stated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "he had received from a researcher in the western part of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "U. S. This letter stated in part as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
