      "text": "\"Dear Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "\"You have often wondered where the 3 men came",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "from that silenced [REDACTED] I",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "answer because 3 men tried to silence [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
